# 🧠 Data Sentinel

![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.10+-blue)
![FastAPI](https://img.shields.io/badge/FastAPI-backend-green)
![PostgreSQL](https://img.shields.io/badge/PostgreSQL-database-blue)
![Streamlit](https://img.shields.io/badge/Streamlit-dashboard-red)
![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/status-active-brightgreen)

> A production-style **data quality, drift detection, and AI observability platform** built with FastAPI, PostgreSQL, and Streamlit.

Transforms raw CSV datasets into structured intelligence through automated profiling, validation, drift detection, and optional LLM-powered analysis.

---

## 🚀 Why this exists

Modern data systems fail silently:
- schema changes break pipelines
- missing values accumulate unnoticed
- distribution drift goes undetected

**Data Sentinel turns every dataset upload into a monitored, versioned intelligence report.**

---

## 🧠 Core Capabilities

### 📊 Data Profiling Engine
- Row / column statistics
- Missing value detection
- Duplicate detection
- Memory footprint estimation
- Automatic schema inference

---

### 🧠 Data Quality Scoring
Each column is classified:

- 🟢 **Good** → clean and usable  
- 🟡 **Warning** → moderate missingness  
- 🔴 **Bad** → fully null or schema issue  

Detects:
- Fully null columns  
- High missing-rate columns (>30%)  
- Unnamed / malformed schema columns  

---

### 🔄 Drift Detection Engine
Tracks dataset evolution over time:

- Schema drift (added / removed columns)
- Type drift (data type changes)
- Distribution drift (mean / std shifts)
- Dataset size change tracking

---

### 🤖 AI Insights Layer (Optional)
LLM-powered interpretation of data health:

- anomaly explanation
- risk summarization
- cleaning recommendations

Graceful fallback modes:
- No API key → disabled safely
- Quota exceeded → non-blocking fallback
- API failure → system continues normally

---

## 🏗️ Architecture
Streamlit Frontend
↓
FastAPI Backend
↓
Pandas / NumPy Processing Layer
↓
PostgreSQL (persistent dataset store)
↓
OpenAI API (optional reasoning layer)

---

